lead_paragraph: Argentina have recalled forward Ezequiel Lavezzi for next month’s South American World Cup qualifiers against Brazil and Colombia despite him not playing since June.

headline.print_headline: Lavezzi Returns to Argentina Squad After Dybala Injury
